title: No. 8 Virginia Tech rallies for 3-2 walk-off win over Middle Tennessee - VT hokiesports.com
content: No. 8 Virginia Tech rallies for 3-2 walk-off win over Middle Tennessee  VT hokiesports.com
description: TUSCALOOSA, Ala. -- The No. 8 Virginia Tech Hokies rallied to score three in the seventh inning and walked it off on freshman Bre Peck's two-run home run off of senior Corrina Dodd to pick up the 3-2 win over Middle Tennessee Friday.
